snippet.title: Mufasa: The Lion King | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A lion who would change our lives forever. #Mufasa: The Lion King, in theaters December 20.

“Mufasa: The Lion King” enlists Rafiki to relay the legend of Mufasa to young lion cub Kiara, daughter of Simba and Nala, with Timon and Pumbaa lending their signature schtick. Told in flashbacks, the story introduces Mufasa as an orphaned cub, lost and alone until he meets a sympathetic lion named Taka—the heir to a royal bloodline. The chance meeting sets in motion an expansive journey of an extraordinary group of misfits searching for their destiny—their bonds will be tested as they work together to evade a threatening and deadly foe.  
 
New and returning cast members were called on to lend their voices to the film:
- Aaron Pierre as Mufasa
- Kelvin Harrison Jr. as Taka, a lion prince with a bright future who accepts Mufasa into his family as a brother
- Tiffany Boone as Sarabi
- Kagiso Lediga as Young Rafiki
- Preston Nyman as Zazu
- Mads Mikkelsen as Kiros, a formidable lion with big plans for his pride 
- Thandiwe Newton as Taka’s mother, Eshe
- Lennie James as Taka’s father, Obasi 
- Anika Noni Rose as Mufasa’s mother, Afia
- Keith David as Mufasa’s father, Masego
- John Kani as Rafiki
- Seth Rogen as Pumbaa
- Billy Eichner as Timon
- Donald Glover as Simba
- Introducing Blue Ivy Carter as Kiara, daughter of King Simba and Queen Nala
- And Beyoncé Knowles-Carter as Nala
 
Additional casting includes Braelyn Rankins, Theo Somolu, Folake Olowofoyeku, Joanna Jones, Thuso Mbedu, Sheila Atim, Abdul Salis and Dominique Jennings.

“Mufasa: The Lion King,” the new film coming to theaters Dec. 20 explores the unlikely rise of the beloved king of the Pride Lands. The film has an all-star roster of talent bringing new and fan-favorite characters to life—plus, celebrated award-winning songwriter Lin-Manuel Miranda is writing the film’s songs produced by Mark Mancina and Miranda, with additional music and performances by Lebo M. 
 
Said Miranda, “Elton John. Tim Rice. Hans Zimmer. Lebo M. Mark Mancina. Beyoncé, Labrinth, Ilya Salmanzadeh. Beau Black, Ford Riley, the incredible music team on ‘The Lion Guard,’ and so many musical contributors over the years. ‘The Lion King’ has an incredible musical legacy with music from some of the greatest songwriters around, and I'm humbled and proud to be a part of it. It's been a joy working alongside Barry Jenkins to bring Mufasa's story to life, and we can't wait for audiences to experience this film in theaters."
 
Blending live-action filmmaking techniques with photoreal computer-generated imagery, “Mufasa: The Lion King” is directed by Barry Jenkins, produced by Adele Romanski & Mark Ceryak, and executive produced by Peter Tobyansen.

snippet.title: Haaland for the Win! Clash of Clans x Erling Haaland
snippet.description:
Gear up for an action-packed season with Erling Haaland! Team up with the best football attacker and lead your troops to victory! 

"Clash With Haaland" season begins May 1st 08:00 AM UTC, and it brings a bunch of exciting events, challenges, temporary units, and football-themed cosmetics - including a skin of KING HAALAND! 


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

https://supercell.com/en/parents/

Mastering Organic Chemistry in 1 Shot! Dive into essential concepts, tricks, and the most important questions for NEET 2024 preparation. Elevate your understanding and excel in Organic Chemistry with confidence! 🌟
-------------------------------------------------------
Batch Description

01. We will cover Physics, Chemistry, Botany, and Zoology.
02. Classes will be conducted for 7 days.
03. One  Lecture per day according to the schedule.
04. We will cover crisp theory, and question discussion via NEET Reflection.
05. Classes will be LIVE on the Physics Wallah - Alakh Pandey Channel.
06. PDF Notes of each Class will be uploaded on the PW App under NEET End Game Batch 2024.
07. It will cover NEET PYQs 
08. Free 3 NEET Replica Full Syllabus Test Series with their LIVE paper Discussion on Competition Wallah YT Channel.
09. The complete course will be accessible to all the students until the NEET 2024 Exam.
10. Classes starting from 27th April 2024.
11. Syllabus will end by 3rd May 2024.
12. The Lecture Schedule will be provided in the community post of  Physics Wallah - Alakh Pandey/Competition Wallah YT Channel and Announcement section of the Batch 
-------------------------------------------------------
Timestamp-
00:00 - Introduction 
02:29 - IUPAC Nomenclature 
40:20 - Isomerism 
2:20:17 - General Organic Chemistry 
4:47:35 - Purification and Quantitative and Qualitative analysis 
5:18:55 - Hydrocarbons 
7:04:50 - Haloalkanes and Haloarenes
7:37:05 - Grignard reagent 
8:13:04 - Alcohols, Phenols and Ethers
9:13:52 - Aldehydes, Ketones and Carboxylic acid 
10:03:52 - Amines and Diazonium salts
11:03:40 - Biomolecules 
11:36:56 - Practical Organic Chemistry 
11:45:20 - Name Reactions 
11:49:35 - Thank You Bachhon!

snippet.title: Mahindra XUV 3XO - XUV300 Pro Max? | First Look
snippet.description: Here's all you need to know about the newly launched Mahindra XUV3X0 which is essentially a mid-life update of the XUV300. Though it still has the same platform and engine options, it now gets several new features including ADAS level 2, 360 degree camera, 6-airbags and ESC as standard, new 17-inch alloy wheels and a new 6-speed automatic gearbox. It also has received major changes on the inside, thanks to the new 10.3-inch touchscreen display with harmon kardon music system, electronic parking brake, 65Watt supported type C among others. All these features make it one of the most loaded cars in its segment. And the best part is its revised pricing, despite newer features it costs less than before as it starts at Rs 7.49 lacs and the top-end variant costs Rs 15.49 lacs (ex-showroom).

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 48 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 27th April 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum
Asma Abbas as Durdana
Behroz Sabzwari as Sheikh Furqan
Zainab Qayoom as Dil Araa
Shehryar Zaidi as Taufeeq
Adnan Samad as Nasir
Sheherzade Peerzada as Hamna  
Minsa Malik as Laiba 
Kinza Malik as Atiya
Mehmood Akhtar as Zaawar

Hamzah Tariq as Rufi

Shiddat Episode 25 [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Anmol Baloch - Digitally Presented by PEL - 29th April 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Shiddat Digitally Presented by PEL

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4071: Taarak's Boss In The Mall
--------------------------------------------------------
All the wives accompany their husbands for a shopping trip. Sodhi jokes with Taarak about Taarak's boss being at the mall, unaware that Taarak's boss is actually there. What might happen if Taarak's boss sees him at the mall?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 4071, 29 April 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: Mr. Wrong | Episode 02 | Turkish Drama | Bay Yanlis | 28 April 2024
snippet.description:
Mr. Wrong also called Bay Yanlis is a Turkish Drama in Urdu Dubbing

🎉 Subscribe   @Urdu1Officialchannel     Youtube Channel and don't forget to click the Bell icon , you'll be the first to know about our new uploads, behind-the-scenes content . Join us on this journey, and let's create amazing memories together!

 #urdu1 # MRWrong # BayYanlis

Join Ezgi, a woman with a tumultuous romantic past, and her new neighbor Asghar, a charming playboy, in a whirlwind of emotions as they navigate the complexities of love and friendship. 

Ezgi's relentless pursuit of the perfect partner often leads to heartbreak, as she prioritizes her partners above herself. Enter Asghar, whose carefree attitude towards relationships offers a fresh perspective. When Asghar offers to coach Ezgi in finding lasting love, their initial friendship takes an unexpected turn. 

As they embark on this journey together, they'll discover hidden desires and confront their own insecurities. Will their unspoken attraction blossom into something more, or will their differences drive them apart? 

Tune in to witness the highs and lows of their emotional rollercoaster as they learn valuable lessons about love, friendship, and self-discovery. Don't miss out on the heartwarming story of Ezgi and Asghar as they unravel the mysteries of the heart.

snippet.description:

Shiddat Episode 26 Teaser - 29th April 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4071 - Musibat Me Phasa Taarak?! I Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

snippet.title: क्या वक़्त पर Jethalal पहुँचेगा Society Compound? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony SAB Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

The members of the Gokuldham society are prepared to leave on their unexpected journey. Even though Jethalal is still not ready, everyone is still waiting. When the bus arrives, every member of the society boards it to go to their unexpected destination. Everyone was taken aback when Jethalal took them to an unidentified place adjacent to the Statue of Unity, the highest statue in the world. Everyone is thrilled and eager to take part in the kite festival. Members of the Gokuldham society have gathered at the Statue of Unity to take part in the 2019 International Kite Festival in honor of Makar Sankranti. Members of the Gokuldham society celebrate unity in front of the world's highest statue, a breathtaking sight.

Show Name: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah 
Star Cast: Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt 
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi 

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #sab #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son, he calls his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal. 

Click here to watch more episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7a-p97oXBuuoyLMAq7Ktx_h
 
क्या वक़्त पर Jethalal पहुँचेगा Society Compound? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

snippet.title: Jetha ने मांगा अपने Soda में Extra नींबू | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Soda Shop Par Charcha
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Tapu Sena comes to discuss the New Year’s party with Bhide. Since Gokuldham Society is getting a fresh coat of paint, Bhide tells them that they cannot waste any money on the event. Meanwhile, Jethalal gets to know about his friend’s vacant apartment, and he secretly plans a party with all the other men from Gokuldham Society. They all are excited about the party. Will they be able to trick all the Gokuldham ladies? 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 511
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the episodes of 'Abdul Ke Soda Shop Par Charcha' : 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTVYwof4_eGQ1-BEtZECY2N

Jetha ने मांगा अपने Soda में Extra नींबू | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Soda Shop Par Charcha

snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu  Grahanam (solar Eclipse)  MCM

Filmymoji middle class Madhu releases it's new Episode what's up Grahanam. In this new Episode of Filmymoji, it starts with conversation between 1A master and his wife bhagyam about Washing machine. 1A master then calls to Washing machine repair man and then he forwards a what's app video to 1A master.  1A master will share this to whole colony and everyone believes it.  Watch the whole episode to enjoy the Grahanam to know what happened really!

Episode 4070: Taarak's Shopping Trip
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak arrives at the mall for the shopping trip. However, he is afraid of his boss showing up at the mall. Later, Taarak's boss calls him to ask about the poem. What will Taarak do now?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
